actions.text: Measure called up by unanimous consent in Senate.

official_title: A resolution to authorize the Secretary of the Senate to make certain transfers of appropriations.

summary.text: Authorizes the Secretary of the Senate to transfer funds from the fiscal year ending June 30, 1976, to pay the contingent expenses of the Senate included under "Inquiries and Investigations" and "Miscellaneous Items." Directs the Secretary to reimburse transferred funds out of future funds made available for disbursement for the fiscal year ending June 30, 1976.
